text: We ordered carbonara and fish and chips. Overall, both dishes are OK for it's price. The carbonara isn't too salty but less creamy while the fish n chips quite delicious

Overall the food is OK, just that I recently ordered a beef steak, they only do it well done, no other choice, its a red flag but I still went with it. The beef looks funny. Seems like many pieces glues together to form a pc. I have never seen a butterfly steak, u can peel the steak into 2 to 3 layers. Taste wise, its very salty. Will avoid the beef in future.
$9.90 promo whole chicken set very nice. Not too dry. Just wish the chilli powder can add more so it's spicier
Surprise find ! Not too salty , just nice and super crispy and aromatic.  Now on offer 9.9 for one chicken chop into 8 pieces, super valued for money.
I orders steak and it is salty and doesn’t look like steak. I don’t even know how to make do of it.  Better to avoid it. Maybe SFA should check on the quality of meat
